hardcorevisor (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Dual VMM backend: rustvmm + qemu with automatic selection
  * REST API + gRPC control plane with full service coverage
  * Virtio block/net device emulation with io_uring async I/O
  * ZFS storage driver, nftables networking, VFIO passthrough
  * etcd-based HA clustering with leader election and fencing
  * Swagger UI API documentation serving
  * hcvctl CLI with man page generation
  * Prometheus metrics + Grafana dashboards + alerting rules
  * 189 automated tests (82 Rust + 107 Go)

